{"tid":1183385,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英35歲男子車禍撞傷下體　持續勃起9天沒痛感","createTime":"2019-06-03T01:05:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T01:07:53.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f4c8c7dc7af691d05895d7284b21aec1807811cb","tid":1183385,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:05:40.000Z","msg":"英國一名35歲男子遭遇車禍並撞傷下體，導致陰莖持續勃起9天，不過沒有痛感，「只是走路時有點不舒服」。醫師依照男子的意願進行手術處理，他的陰莖勃起功能在一年後才回復正常。<br />\n英國修南安普敦大學醫院（University Hospital Southampton）上月在泌尿外科病例報告中談及這起個案，指病人是騎小型機車出意外後傷及下體，而當時陰莖屬於勃起硬度指數（EHS）中的第四級別，即最堅硬的勃起狀態，然而沒有痛楚。他見情況持續了好幾天，決定求醫。<br />\n醫師表示，他的陰囊及會陰有瘀血，導致血液被困在陰莖引發陰莖持續勃起症（Priapism），如果沒有及時治療可導致留疤或永久性勃起功能障礙。<br />\n報告指出，有60%陰莖持續勃起症的患者可以自行痊癒，不過本個案患者決定接受手術治療，陰莖勃起功能也在一年後才回復正常。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190603/640_acd2198fca07ea390af774e83c07ed25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190603%2F640_acd2198fca07ea390af774e83c07ed25.jpg&h=55fc9620&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190603/1577563/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190603%2F1577563%2F&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOJFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=c1ab0baa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190603%2F1577563%2F&h=1d8e7b60\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190603/1577563/</a>"},{"pid":"9fe7ed625070ac96a734a20398385603defc82f7","tid":1183385,"uid":189109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:07:53.000Z","msg":"瘋狂屌閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}